text: Yuki Bhambri was the Traralgon Champion from 2013, but he did not compete that year, while Bradley Klahn was current Traralgon Champion, having won the first of two challengers held in this place in 2014, but he lost to Benjamin Mitchell in the first round. John Millman won the title, defeating James Ward in the final, 6–4, 6–1. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Finals=== ===Top Half=== ===Bottom Half=== ==References== * Main Draw * Qualifying Draw Category:2014 ATP Challenger Tour 2014 Singles Category:2014 in Australian tennis
